app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/2079-4991/11/3/569/s1, Figure S1: SEM images for different ALD coating layers: (a) SVO-0, (b) SVO-10, (c) SVO-50, (d) SVO-100 after 100 charge–discharge cycles at a current density of 50 mA g −1; Figure S2: EDX spectrum taken from the (a) SVO-0, (b) SVO-100 after 100 charge-discharge cycles; Figure S3: CV curves of (a) SVO-0, (b) SVO-10, (c) SVO-50, (d) SVO-100 at a scanning rate of 0.2 mV s −1 in the third cycle; Figure S4: Bode plots for SVO-0, SVO-10, SVO-50, SVO-100 after (a) 0 (b) 10, (c) 20, (d) 50 battery cycles; Table S1: Values of resistance calculated from fitting the impedance graphs.
